The folder minesweeper has all the compiled java files

Start the server as follows:
open terminal or cmd window
cd to the correct folder
run the following:
"java minesweeper.server.MinesweeperServer --port 4444"
   possibly add other options like: "--size x y", "--file filename" 
   (see the java files for details)

Connect as client by entering in a different terminal/cmd window:
telnet 127.0.0.1 4444 (for local clients)
or:
telnet 192.168.1.173 4444 (example of local network clients)